      • addDevelopment

        int[] addDevelopment(CardImpl dev)
        Adds the development card to player's deck, adds player's permanent gems based on the card's provided permanent gem, also finally return the payment (to pay GameBoard). For the payment, the method will first check if gold is ever used, if true then subtract the payment gems by 1 (use gold). Return the payment.
        Parameters:
        dev -
        Returns:
        payment for GameBoard
